{
  "texts": [
    "The LLMs demonstrate remarkable abilities to perform tasks based on user prompts and rapidly adapt to new scenarios through in-context learning.",
    "Zhou et al.",
    "highlighted the intrinsic properties of LLMs that facilitate this adaptability, laying the groundwork for their application as complex agents [22].",
    "The shift towarded employing LLMs as the \"brain\" or controller of agents, as discussed by Xi et al., signified a pivotal transition towards more integrated and autonomous systems [23].",
    "introduced AssistGPT, which employed a method of linguistic reasoning called Plan, Do, Check, and Learn (PEIL)."
  ]
}